    "The covariates for Effect year",
    "and Data age vary both within and between the 40 database clusters.",
    "To distinguish between the within database cluster and between database cluster effects of these covariates, we centered the variables (Fisher & Tipton, 2015; Tanner-Smith & Tipton, 2014).",
    "m_Effect year and m_Data age provide estimates of between-database effects whereas c_Effect year and c_Data age provide estimates of within-database effects.",
    "See Table 2 wvariables."
  ],
